just answer the question!

28
00:02:10,631 --> 00:02:12,101
The defendant would be you.

29
00:02:13,231 --> 00:02:15,201
I've never been unfaithful to my partner.

30
00:02:15,341 --> 00:02:16,301
You liar!

31
