But that really brings back memories.

44
00:02:46,831 --> 00:02:49,531
Those days were the peak of
my popularity in my life.

45
00:02:50,171 --> 00:02:52,231
My popularity with the girls
has plummeted as of late.

46
00:02:52,571 --> 00:02:54,441
Then if you were still popular,
you'd fool around, right?

47
00:02:56,711 --> 00:02:57,711
I wouldn't.

48
00:02:57,711 --> 00:03:00,041
Why not?
Because you're afraid of Junko?

49
00:03:00,251 --> 00:03:01,651
Well sure, it's natural to be
afraid of Junko,

50
00:03:01,651 --> 00:03:02,781
being a former delinquent in school
and all.

51
00:03:04,121 --> 00:03:05,981
Because I'm afraid of losing Junko.

52
